{"tid":2082297,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如何霸氣地反駁「有國才有家」 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-06-28T02:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T02:58:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9819ce714a07f4e95eb9bbbab801efa5e599f8","tid":2082297,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:34:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200628/20945445/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200628%2F20945445%2F&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtKjakGblTMbnvy6EODhsvCk%3D&h=7dc1d2c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200628%2F20945445%2F&h=6dc14caa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200628/20945445/</a><br />\n<br />\n如何霸氣地反駁「有國才有家」 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200628/large/1593249790_d077.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200628%2Flarge%2F1593249790_d077.jpg&h=9610c5ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（網上截圖）<br />\n<br />\n是日心情不爽，又禍不單行，在飯局碰上一個持加拿大護照的律屍J大放厥詞，講什麼「有國先至有家吖嘛，梗係支持國安法啦」，一向保持中立兼港豬形象的我，決定今天獎勵一下自己，懲罰一下對方，暫緩「沉默是金」原則，攞呢位「愛國」律屍出一出悶氣。<br />\n<br />\n我堆起笑容問道：「J律屍，嗱我就唔識政治，不過啲死廢青一聽到『沒有國哪有家』就唔順超，你識咁多嘢，不如教吓我哋點樣駁啲廢青都好吖，到底『沒有國哪有家』係點解究呢？」J好像有點詫異我有此一問，連忙托一托眼鏡，猶豫兩三秒才說：「好簡單啫，國家、國家吖嘛，有名你叫，咁國同家點可以分離呢？」<br />\n<br />\n我拍案說：「嘩，咁講法你咪食屎！」眾人都紛紛向我投以好奇眼光，律屍J也秒答：「點解呀？」我說：「你專做離婚官司㗎嘛，夫妻、夫妻，有名你叫啦，咁夫同妻又點會離婚呢？冇人離婚，你仲唔食屎咩？」他一時想不出怎樣答，只好先喝一口茶。所謂「敵疲我打，敵退我追」，我連忙向J做個道歉手勢，說道：「唔好意思唔好意思，粗人呀，我哋呢啲係粗人，講嘢吳京大腦。不如你講返點解『沒有國哪有家』先啦，我仲未get到呀！」<br />\n<br />\n律屍徐徐放下手中茶杯，以舌尖潤一潤嘴脣才說：「嗱，<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n彷彿一個在舞台上表演完畢的演員，躊躇滿志等待歡呼和掌聲。<br />\n<br />\n這時候我又拍一拍枱，有點激動地說：「。。。。。。。。。<br />\n，咪變相幫港獨搖旗吶喊，想累死我咩？」<br />\n<br />\n律屍J也老羞成怒：「。。。。。。。<br />\n色列，佢哋都有其他國籍㗎嘛，咁咪即係點都要有個國囉！」<br />\n<br />\n我說：「你咁講法<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n關你咩事呀？<br />\n<br />\n「再答返你第一條<br />\n。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n見J律屍鐵青着臉，我連忙做個道歉手勢，笑道：「唔好意思唔好意思，粗人呀，我哋呢啲係粗人，講嘢吳京大腦，不如大家都係食飯先啦，飲杯飲杯！」 <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n============<br />\n<br />\n笑到黐線， 大家一定要睇下。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b02d0fa13307543a9ab001fbf964e557025ae9","tid":2082297,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440ba9887c48b8fe59566ae3a482fee61ed03bb3","tid":2082297,"uid":67028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"有人才有國"},{"pid":"1f536e8d9681b600ed60ed58e50ce9e67824f173","tid":2082297,"uid":165184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T02:58:11.000Z","msg":"駁藍絲「有國先有家」定「有家先有國」<br />\n好簡單<br />\n<br />\n對文學淺藍<br />\n修身、齊家、治國、平天下<br />\n要齊家先可以治國<br />\n所以有家先有國<br />\n<br />\n對理科淺藍<br 